course_description:
BIOS 517D is the follow-up course to BIOS 516D. BIOS 516D ended with procedures for two independent samples (two sample t-test and chi-square test). This course starts with procedures for paired samples, nonparametric tests and power/size calculations. Students then begin their study of linear regression, starting with zero-predictor models, one-predictor models and then moving on to multiple-predictor models and ANOVA.
